OL,3,CFive dead after shooting in northern
OL,4,CGermany, police say
OL,6,FFive people have been killed in a
OL,7,Fshooting on Monday in the northern
OL,8,FGerman town of Stade, police have said.
OL,10,FLocal police confirmed two suspects
OL,11,Fhave been arrested. A motive for the
OL,12,Fattack is not yet clear.
OL,14,FInformation regarding the victims or
OL,15,Fthe motive of the shooting is not yet
OL,16,Fknown.
