OL,3,CFive dead after shooting in northern
OL,4,CGermany, police say
OL,6,FPolice said the shooting took place
OL,7,Fnear a youth facility, prompting a
OL,8,Fmajor police operation on
OL,9,FDankersstrasse, south of the town
OL,10,Fcentre.
OL,12,FFive people are dead and others have
OL,13,Fsustained injuries.
OL,15,FPosting on social media platform X,
OL,16,FLuneburg Police said "an operation is
OL,17,Fcurrently taking place in Stade" and
OL,18,Fthat members of the public should
OL,19,Favoid the area.
