OL,3,CFive dead after shooting in northern
OL,4,CGermany, police say
OL,6,FStade is a town located around 40
OL,7,Fkilometers west of Hamburg with a
OL,8,Fpopulation of around 50,000 people.
OL,10,FAn investigation is ongoing. Police
OL,11,Fsay there is "no danger to the public."
